":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T10:28:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實鬥遲走依個風氣真係好戇鳩<br />\n應該要由我地年輕一代改變歪風</blockquote><br />\n夠鐘就唔撚使理佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d1fec08e69095a22e4d7d9fc714126bc14d68c0","tid":459941,"uid":140182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T07:00:47.000Z","msg":"最戇鳩係有時要做嘢遲咗啲走，啲老屎忽就走過黎寸鳩我話 咦你仲未走嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我真係想屌鳩佢話 係呀，咁又點撚樣呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65e7f13ffcfebf030f7c52f88c982d532509a531","tid":459941,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T07:12:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最戇鳩係有時要做嘢遲咗啲走，啲老屎忽就走過黎寸鳩我話 咦你仲未走嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我真係想屌鳩佢話 係呀，咁又點撚樣呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁弱雞架你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}